SUMMARY:Autocross/Solo — Event #4 — Ejecto Seato Cones
LOCATION:Burleson High School
DESCRIPTION:Texas SCCA Solo Event #4. Championship points event. Jeff is Tech Inspection Co-Chair — arrive early for setup.
CATEGORIES:Racing,Autocross
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:txscca-2026-e4-maint@hermes-racing
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260503
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260510
SUMMARY:MODS / MAINTENANCE — Ejecto Seato Cones
DESCRIPTION:Week-long maintenance window. Focus: brake pads\, alignment\, coolant\, tires\, any BSP-legal mods. Target event: Autocross/Solo — Event #4 — Ejecto Seato Cones. Jeff works M–F 8–5\; kid activities weeknights. Mods happen this weekend.
CATEGORIES:Maintenance,Racing
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:txscca-2026-e4-prep@hermes-racing
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260510
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260517
SUMMARY:PREP / PACK / SIM — Ejecto Seato Cones
DESCRIPTION:Week-long prep window. Focus: fine-tuning setup\, virtual seat time on sim rig\, packing tools/gear\, tire pressures\, alignment confirmation. Target event: Autocross/Solo — Event #4 — Ejecto Seato Cones. Prep happens this weekend.\n\nTECH INSPECTION CO-CHAIR: Saturday night is EARLY BEDTIME. No late activities. Arrive at venue early Sunday morning for tech setup.
CATEGORIES:Car Prep,Racing
END:VEVENT
