DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260518
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260526
SUMMARY:Tire Sale Watch — Memorial Day Weekend
DESCRIPTION:Memorial Day weekend historically brings tire discounts. Watch for deals on Bridgestone RE71RZ 275/35R18 (200+ treadwear DOT\, BSP-legal). Check Tire Rack\, Discount Tire\, and other major retailers daily this week.
CATEGORIES:Shopping,Racing
END:VEVENT
