BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:annualtech-2027-locations@hermes-racing
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270101
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270201
SUMMARY:Annual Tech Planning — Locations & Venues
DESCRIPTION:January = annual tech inspection planning season. As Tech Inspection Co-Chair\, Jeff needs to scout and confirm locations for annual tech sessions. Coordinate with Texas SCCA Solo chair on venue availability\, garage partnerships\, and inspection bay layout. Jeff works M–F 8–5\; planning calls and site visits happen on weekends.
CATEGORIES:Tech Inspection,Racing
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:annualtech-2027-timing@hermes-racing
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20270201
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20270301
SUMMARY:Annual Tech Planning — Timing & Logistics
DESCRIPTION:February = annual tech inspection logistics lock-in. As Tech Inspection Co-Chair\, Jeff needs to finalize dates\, build the inspection schedule\, recruit volunteer inspectors\, and publish the annual tech calendar to the region. Confirm registration deadlines and MotorsportReg setup. Jeff works M–F 8–5\; coordination happens on weekends.
CATEGORIES:Tech Inspection,Racing
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR